photos.name: South African Eiffel tower
photos.description: As part of the South African season in France, the Eiffel Tower will be lit in the colors of South Africa from May 28th to June 2nd, then from June 15th to June 16th (Youth Day in South Africa) and from July 15th to July 21st, at the occasion of the Nelson Mandela International day. (http://www.tour-eiffel.fr)

photos.name: La Majestueuse de Paris. 2008
photos.description: D’une hauteur de 312 mètreso 1 à l’origine, la tour Eiffel est restée le monument le plus élevé du monde pendant 41 ans.
